<h2 class="sectionedit1"><a name="asctime" id="asctime">asctime</a></h2>
<div class="level2">

<p>
语法：
</p>
<pre class="cpp code cpp">    <span class="co2">#include &lt;ctime&gt;</span>
    <span class="kw4">char</span> <span class="sy2">*</span><span class="kw3">asctime</span><span class="br0">&#40;</span> <span class="kw4">const</span> <span class="kw4">struct</span> <span class="kw4">tm</span> <span class="sy2">*</span>ptr <span class="br0">&#41;</span><span class="sy4">;</span></pre>
<p>

函数 asctime() 将结构体 &#039;ptr&#039; 中存放的时间变换为以下格式的字符串：
</p>
<pre class="cpp code cpp">     年 月 日 小时：分钟：秒 年</pre>
<p>

一个例子：
</p>
<pre class="cpp code cpp">     Mon Jun <span class="nu0">26</span> <span class="nu0">12</span><span class="sy4">:</span><span class="nu8">03</span><span class="sy4">:</span><span class="nu0">53</span> <span class="nu0">2000</span></pre>
<p>
相关主题： <a href="clock" class="wikilink1" title="cn:chrono:c:clock">clock</a>, <a href="ctime" class="wikilink1" title="cn:chrono:c:ctime">ctime</a>, <a href="difftime" class="wikilink1" title="cn:chrono:c:difftime">difftime</a>, <a href="gmtime" class="wikilink1" title="cn:chrono:c:gmtime">gmtime</a>, <a href="localtime" class="wikilink1" title="cn:chrono:c:localtime">localtime</a>, <a href="mktime" class="wikilink1" title="cn:chrono:c:mktime">mktime</a>, <a href="time" class="wikilink1" title="cn:chrono:c:time">time</a>
</p>

